snippet.title: Kay's Destiny Official Trailer
snippet.description:
▼▼INFO & USEFUL LINKS▼▼

► STEAM PAGE: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2335640/Kays_Destiny/

Kay's Destiny is a retro style tribut JRPG developed by KayThePianist.
It features an original story, and open world with backtracking and sidequests, and a original live piano soundtrack.

Wishlist on Steam!
